
<p>I've put up a video expanding on my <a target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gKumet6b-WY">i3blocks status bar</a>, partially in preparation for the LARBS tutorial videos.</p>

<p>I've implemented many new features, including signaling for a lower footprint bar, and some other bells and whistles. I also go through where everything is in the system for people using my configs.</p>
